=head1 DESCRIPTION

Determines which tools the model should request in a call to
C<Converse> or C<ConverseStream>. C<ToolChoice> is only supported by
Anthropic Claude 3 models and by Mistral AI Mistral Large.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Any => L<Paws::BedrockRuntime::AnyToolChoice>

The model must request at least one tool (no text is generated).


=head2 Auto => L<Paws::BedrockRuntime::AutoToolChoice>

(Default). The Model automatically decides if a tool should be called
or whether to generate text instead.


=head2 Tool => L<Paws::BedrockRuntime::SpecificToolChoice>

The Model must request the specified tool. Only supported by Anthropic
Claude 3 models.



